.4504, 183.6926, 180.2768, 177.2356, 176.736, 176.9925, 176.8608, 176.0428, 175.3366, 173.9382, 173.8801, 175.3572, 177.1646, 176.7506, 177.5484, 178.6277, 180.9393, 180.0013, 180.0446, 179.9744, 180.2001, 181.9148, 183.162, 183.2914, 183.7213, 182.579, 182.0294, 181.2444, 181.5808, 183.2823, 182.6622, 182.2747, 180.7087, 181.3271, 182.7282, 182.8757, 182.5551, 183.5118, 183.1313, 183.2144, 182.1694, 181.4304, 181.4766, 181.7333, 180.4502, 179.4358, 180.0621, 179.396, 179.7403, 178.6072, 177.4607, 178.1881, 176.9296, 176.1182, 177.0424, 176.5333, 174.219, 173.7227, 174.8493, 173.2643, 174.8895, 174.5645, 174.4805, 173.1831, 169.4526, 169.8128, 171.0408, 168.9275, 164.7264, 165.0506, 161.4012, 160.6446, 164.9534, 165.4288, 165.1827, 163.9069, 165.4704, 159.931, 159.9918, 159.6406, 158.6351, 155.5562, 160.7228, 165.076, 162.1138, 160.9691, 164.8807, 164.2496, 162.025, 161.4177, 157.686, 159.7756, 157.9492, 155.9589, 154.4925, 155.8893, 155.0972, 154.5415, 160.8139, 158.5588, 160.7538, 162.4606, 163.6292, 163.2324, 163.6333, 163.5037, 166.0784, 167.1907, 167.3552, 166.967, 170.264, 169.7067, 169.5819, 168.5488, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>盈利偏度和估值偏度因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.376)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告研究了股票基本面信息偏度（盈利偏度和估值偏度）对横截面收益的预测能力。盈利偏度（如ROA/营业利润率过去8季度的偏度）正向预测收益；估值偏度（PE/POP过去252日的偏度）负向预测收益。移植到商品期货时，核心逻辑为：计算价值比（close/MA）的滚动偏度作为估值偏度的类比。低偏度品种（历史上频繁出现极端低估值）倾向于被低估，未来获得更高收益——这是基本面延迟反应和低估值风险补偿的共同结果。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.92</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3140</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.28</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-1.32</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.06 / 1.47</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.64</td><td>1.73</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.17</span></td><td>0.78</td><td>1.21</td><td>1.19</td><td>1.21</td><td>1.24</td><td>1.29</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.73</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td>0.11</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.57</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3142</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{val\\_ratio}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{close}_{i,t}}{\\text{MA}_{300}(\\text{close}_{i,t})}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Skew}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{T}\\sum_{s=t-T+1}^{t}\\left(\\frac{r_s - \\bar{r}}{\\hat{\\sigma}}\\right)^3, \\quad T = 252</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">r_s = \\text{val\\_ratio}_{i,s}</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\bar{r}</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat{\\sigma}</span> 分别为窗口内的均值和标准差。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = -\\text{Skew}(\\text{val\\_ratio}_{i}, 252)</div>\n<p>负号表示低偏度品种做多、高偏度品种做空。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>首轮12变体。val_skew252_h21_raw 1.07通过，ret_skew正方向全部失败</td><td>实现核心因子：收益率偏度(4窗口)+价值比偏度(3窗口)+组合因子</td><td>Sharpe 1.066, 通过backtest gate</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>val_skew252是唯一强信号，ret_skew方向错误</td><td>翻转ret_skew方向为负；加IC gate；加180d窗口；触发cs/ts归一化</td><td>Sharpe 1.133 (cs版提升)。IC gate无效（被dedup）</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>需优化MA分母和skew窗口；val_skew252是核心</td><td>参数网格：MA{200,252,300} x Skew{200,252,300} x Hold{10,21}；加hold 10d</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.376</strong>。MA300+Skew252+Hold10为最优组合</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R3 中将 hold_days 从 21 缩短至 10 是最大提升来源（1.07 -&gt; 1.38），因为偏度信号衰减较快，短持仓更好捕捉均值回复效应。MA300（vs 252）使价值比分母更平滑，减少噪声。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（69个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>信号逻辑</strong>: 截面因子，低偏度品种做多/高偏度品种做空</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 原报告为股票因子，移植到商品期货时盈利偏度（收益率偏度）效果较弱，估值偏度（价值比偏度）是主要alpha来源。短窗口skew（&lt;120d）和长hold（&gt;21d）效果较差。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>MA_W</code></td><td><code>300</code></td><td>MA window for value ratio</td></tr><tr><td><code>SKEW_W</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>skewness window</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>21</code></td><td>hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>DIRECTION</code></td><td><code>-1.0</code></td><td>low skew = bullish</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9953</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.19s</li>\n</ul>"}